organic_results.title: Participation in sport as related to educational expectations among high school girls
organic_results.snippet: This paper analyzes the relationship between extracurricular participation and educational expectations among high school girls. The analysis focuses on athletic participation and serious involvement in music as socialization experiences within the school context. There is an association between both types of extracurricular participation and educational expectations, but the findings also revealed differences according to the type of interscholastic sport in which the girls were participating.
